- **Compliance Frameworks**: Ad-hoc implementation with no formal compliance (e.g., ISO 27001) or interoperability standards (e.g., OPC UA).
- **Interoperability Standards**: None adopted; data exchange occurs via custom protocols (e.g., ActiveMQ messages).

The **Air Quality Management** exemplar complies with:
